Description: Sailor Moon fights for justice in the name of the Moon and the mysterious Moon Princess. Along the way, she recruits other girls to be Sailor Scouts and join her fight against evil.
Title: SAILOR MOON, VOL. 4
Author: Naoko Takeuchi

Description: Naruto is in the middle of a great war — and the opposing side has a horde of animated dead ninjas.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 55
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: The Fairy Tail are a group of powerful wizards.
Title: FAIRY TAIL, VOL. 18
Author: Hiro Mashima

Description: The world of the popular video game series provides the setting for the adventures of Shiki, a young man who will travel to the ends of the earth to hunt legendary monsters.
Title: MONSTER HUNTER ORAGE, VOL. 4
Author: Hiro Mashima

Description: Graduation is just around the corner for the Tokyo Space School's first class.
Title: TWIN SPICA, VOL. 12
Author: Kou Yaginuma

Description: Misao Harada can see into a magical realm where she is the bride demon of prophecy.
Title: BLACK BIRD, VOL. 13
Author: Kanoko Sakurakoji

Description: Naruto, who wants to be a great ninja, is locked in a battle to decide the fate of the land.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 54
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: The Pokemon saga continues with the introduction of two new trainers: Black and White.
Title: POKEMON BLACK AND WHITE, VOL. 5
Author: Hidenori Kusaka

Description: Monkey D. Luffy and his motley crew of would-be pirates search for a legendary treasure called “One Piece.” In this volume, the crew decide to train harder. The reward? New enemies and adventures.
Title: ONE PIECE, VOL. 61
Author: Eiichiro Oda

Description: Maka, an arms expert, wants to turn the Soul Eater, her living scythe, into the ultimate weapon for Death.
Title: SOUL EATER, VOL. 8
Author: Atsushi Ohkubo
